  There are different definitions of connectedness that are classicaly
  equivalent.
</fr:p><fr:p>
  The <fr:link
href="axt-000E.xml"
type="local"
addr="axt-000E">standard definition</fr:link> is the one that says a space is connected
  if no separation for it exists.
</fr:p><fr:tree
